events.text:
Our brethren have fallen from venomous sting of those flying bugs that you'll find south of here.
The cure of the sting comes from the venom extracted from their stingers. However we are critically low in supplies of the antidote.
Collect the stingers from those flying buzzards and bring them back to me.
Have you got those stingers? Those flying buzzards have been poisoning our people.
Glad you have these here stingers, what was your reward again?
